videos.description: Elijah Stewart drives and dumps it off to Nick Rakocevic who dunks it home.
videos.headline: USC's Rakocevic sends home two-handed dunk

videos.description: Bennie Boatwright shows off some nice moves to score plus a foul.
videos.headline: USC's Boatwright uses the spin on and-1 layup

videos.description: Jemerrio Jones passes it up to Zack Lofton who hits the 3-pointer for Aggies.
videos.headline: New Mexico State steal leads to Lofton 3-pointer

videos.description: A.J. Harris' block leads to a Sidy N'Dir 3-pointer on the other end for Aggies.
videos.headline: New Mexico State block sets up N'Dir 3-pointer

videos.description: Johnny McCants snatches a lob pass out of the air with his back to the basket and still scores.
videos.headline: New Mexico State's McCants scores off lob with one hand

videos.description: Eli Chuha rises up to score the basket off the missed shot.
videos.headline: New Mexico State's  Chuha makes put-back shot

videos.description: Chimezie Metu blocks the shot allowing Jonah Matthews to score the game-tying layup late in 2nd half.
videos.headline: USC turns block into lay-in to tie game

videos.description: Bennie Boatwright hits the game-clinching 3-pointer to cap off his career-high 33 point performance in the Trojans win.
videos.headline: USC's Boatwright drains deep 3-pointer to seal win

videos.description: Bennie Boatwright talks about his big performance in the championship of the Diamond Head Classic as well as being named MVP of the tournament.
videos.headline: Boatwright breaks down career game in win for USC
